# NexusDeploy - Enterprise CI/CD Automation Platform

## 🎯 Project Introduction

**NexusDeploy** is a comprehensive, enterprise-grade **Continuous Integration and Continuous Deployment (CI/CD) automation platform** built on AWS cloud infrastructure. It represents a complete DevOps solution that orchestrates the entire software delivery lifecycle—from source code commits through to production deployment.

---

## 📖 What is NexusDeploy?

NexusDeploy is an integrated CI/CD platform that automates the building, testing, securing, and deploying of containerized applications. It eliminates manual deployment processes, reduces human error, and accelerates software delivery while maintaining security and code quality standards.

By seamlessly connecting GitHub repositories with Jenkins pipelines, code quality analysis through SonarQube, security scanning via Trivy, containerization with Docker, and cloud deployment on AWS ECS Fargate, NexusDeploy provides a complete automation framework for modern DevOps teams.

