## 🏗 Architecture Overview

```
Developer Code Push
        ↓
   GitHub Webhook
        ↓
  Jenkins Pipeline
        ├→ Code Analysis (SonarQube)
        ├→ Security Scan (Trivy)
        ├→ Docker Build
        └→ Push to Registry (ECR)
        ↓
  Amazon ECS Fargate
        ↓
Production Deployment
```

